The briefing(Feb. 13th) on COVID-19 in Republic of Korea
 
○ As of 09:00, 13 February 2020, there have been 28 confirmed cases, 5,099 turned out to be negative, and 670 currently being tested. Out of 1,784 contacts of cases in total, 11 cases has been confirmed.
